            <title>ZEEKR 全港首間陳列室灣仔開幕　 限時展出純電超跑 Zeekr 001 FR</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/zeekr-space-wan-chai/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zeekr-space-wan-chai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/zeekr-space-wan-chai/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:00:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[純電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1234596</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>吉利控股集團旗下電動汽車品牌 Zeekr（極氪）首間香港陳列室 Zeekr Space 今日正式於灣仔開幕投入服務，同場限時展出 1,265 匹馬力純電獵裝超跑 Zeekr 001 FR。全能都市型 SUV Zeekr X (港澳右軚版本) 亦將於本月月下旬抵港。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>陳列室展示 Zeekr 其中兩款隨即在香港上市的型號 Zeekr 009 及 SUV Zeekr X 之餘，更限時展出 1,265 匹馬力的純電獵裝超跑 Zeekr 001 FR。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_8-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_8-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲純電獵裝超跑 Zeekr 001 FR</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_14-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_14-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_14-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲SUV Zeekr X （左）；純電獵裝超跑 Zeekr 001 FR（右）</p><p>Zeekr Space 陳列室配備開放式的洽談區和獨立的洽談室，方便銷售顧問為顧客提供個人化購買體驗。陳列室亦設有品牌精品專區 Zeekr Collection。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_15-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_15-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_15-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_13-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_13-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_13-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_7-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_7-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Zeekr （錦龍汽車）總經理梁栢福表示，為方便客戶，Zeekr Space 特地選址灣仔市中心。據梁栢福透露，稍後預計本年 7 月底在太古城開設第二個陳列室，是 Zeekr 在香港的旗艦「品牌體驗中心」，旨在打造 Zeekr 高端豪華新能源的品牌形象。 集團計劃在 2025 年於香港島，九龍，新界開設陳列室及售後中心，以及增添充電裝置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_12-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_12-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_12-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>地址： 香港灣仔告士打道 39 號夏愨大廈地下 A 舖<br />
服務時間： 星期一至日及公眾假期　上午 9 時正至晚上 8 時正</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-model-3-performance-press-release/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">新 Tesla Model 3 Performance 抵港　破百 3.1 秒 +  528KM 續航力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/bloomberg-said-tesla-baidu-may-work-together-for-tesla-fsd-in-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">彭博：Tesla 與百度將達成協議　協助 Tesla FSD 進入中國市場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/huawei-car-3-dead/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為問界電動車意外焚燬困人釀 3 死　客服查詢售後體驗 + 問界汽車：電池正常</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/zeekr-space-wan-chai/life-tech/auto/">ZEEKR 全港首間陳列室灣仔開幕　 限時展出純電超跑 Zeekr 001 FR</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
