            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>cmf by Nothing 這個 Nothing 初創公司的子品牌，除了早前為大家介紹過的抵玩智能手錶 Watch Pro 外，同期其實亦推出了一款 $400 有找，同樣抵玩的真無線耳機 Buds Pro。定價來説確實是抵玩，但究竟使用起來效果又如何？音質會否有驚喜？就讓 Edward 現在為 unwire.hk 們深入評測一下吧。</p><h2>cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 開箱直擊</h2><p>一如以往，在為大家分享 cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 的使用體驗前，先讓 Edward 為大家來個開箱直擊吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00579-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00579-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00579.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是 cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 的包裝盒，今次借測的有兩種顏色：淺灰色及橙色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00581-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00581-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00581.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00582-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00582-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00582.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲包裝盒上印有產品規格資訊，亦印有它是在中國製造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00583-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00583-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00583.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲與 Watch Pro 一樣，Buds Pro 也是採用揭蓋式設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00584-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00584-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00584.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234547" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00587-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00587-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00587.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左方揭蓋內頁印有耳機構造圖，以及用作掃描下載 Nothing X APP 作配對耳機的 QR Code。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00585-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00585-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00585.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而右方就見到 Buds Pro 耳機充電盒的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00586-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00586-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00586.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而白色的包裝盒內就裝有多兩對大、細耳塞、USB-C 充電線及説明書。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234548 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234549 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲基本上由於 Buds Pro 支援 Google 快速配對功能，如果大家使用的是 Android 手機，即使不安裝 Nothing X APP 也可以配對耳機的，但就用不到 Nothing X APP 內的調校功能了。至於 iPhone，就一定要安裝這個 APP 才可配對得到。</p><h2>佩戴感舒服穩陣不易甩</h2><p>先説外觀設計吧：cmf by Nothing 最新推出的 Buds Pro 真無線耳機，採用了圓形的充電盒，有別於一般真無線耳機採用的長方體圓角設計，加上鮮艷吸引的配色（尤其是橙色），確實十分「吸睛」。耳機體積亦不大，十分輕身，筆者以電子磅量度過一對重量也只是 9.9g，戴在雙耳十分無感，而且耳塞用料柔軟，長時間佩戴耳道亦不覺有不適感。此外，耳機可以十分穩陣佩戴在雙耳上，筆者試過即使跑步或跳動也未試過會甩出來，整體使用體驗都十分理想，完全不像一款 $400 有找的真無線耳機所帶來的體驗感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234554" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00588-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00588-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00588.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是 cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 的充電盒，大家可以見到它採用圓形設計，有別於一般真無線耳機採用較長方形充電盒的風格。當中橙色版本肯定是最為搶眼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00591-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00591-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00591.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充電盒盒底印有 cmf by Nothing 的商標。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234557" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00594-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00594-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00594-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前方設有指示燈，留意揭開時，有燈的一半部分要在下方，揭開時耳機才會穩穩放在充電盒內。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234558" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00593-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00593-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00593.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而背後就設有 USB-C 充電插槽，留意 Buds Pro 只能支援有線充電，不支援無線充電的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00596-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00596-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00596-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲打開充電盒，就見到 Buds Pro 真身了，而耳機配色與充電盒配色是一樣的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00605-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00605-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00605.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳柄內側設有的金屬點具備磁吸功能，放在充電盒合適位置就會吸著並開始充電。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00599-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00599-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00599.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳機設計方面，基本上與一般真無線耳機差不多，不過它的耳柄位就相對較短，令耳機看起來較細隻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00612-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00612-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00612.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234563" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00614-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00614-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00614.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者以電子磅量度，一對耳機的重量也只是 9.9g，十分輕身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00601-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00601-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00601-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳機輕加上體積細，拿在手掌內十分舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164903-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164903-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164903.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即使佩戴在耳朵上，那種輕身程度亦十分無感，而且耳塞物料較為柔軟，長時間佩戴耳道也不會覺得辛苦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00619-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00619-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00619.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00616-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00616-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00616.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而外攜使用時，即使耳機連充電盒，重量也只是 54.9g，仍然十分輕身，放在褲袋亦十分輕鬆。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00603-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00603-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00603.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳柄位同樣印有 cmf by Nothing 的商標，這亦是觸控操控耳機的位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234570" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00606-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00606-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00606.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳機上這個黑點位置設有感應位，可以感測用家是否已戴上耳機，如是就會自動啟動音樂播放等功能。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/cmf-by-nothing-watch-pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】cmf by Nothing Watch Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　屏幕　操控體驗　使用時間開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/cmf-neckband-pro-cmf-buds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 兩款無線耳機   CMF Neckband Pro、CMF Buds With ANC 發表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/23/cmf-by-nothing-neckband-pro/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 兩款無線耳機，確認 3 月 5 日與 Phone (2a) 一同發表</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>音質不過不失低音較遜色</h2><p>至於音質方面，cmf by Nothing 官方未有提及 Buds Pro 採用多大的驅動單元，只是介紹使用了定製的動態低音加強驅動單元，而筆者佩戴後使用，感覺音質算是不錯，高清清晰到位，人聲亦可清楚聽到，不過官方表示的強化低音效果，筆者試聽過就只是一般般，不但動態不太足夠，而且聽起來十分矇，感覺不算理想。不過如果大家用來聽歌時不是欣賞以低音為主的音樂（例如：Jazz、Rock 等），或者用來睇戲聽音效時對音質要求不是太高，Buds Pro 的表現也未至於十分差的。不過它的音頻解碼只支援 AAC 及 SBC，而且亦不支援任何高清音效標準，感覺有點可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00610-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00610-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00610.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Buds Pro 採用了定製式的動態低音加強驅動單元，筆者試聽後聽感算不錯，人聲清晰高音亦到位，不過低音表現就十分一般，即使官方表示加強了低音效果，但聽起來仍然比較矇，不算理想。而且它亦不支援所有高清無線音效標準，有點可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234573" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當然，Nothing X APP 內亦設有低音增強的均衡器設定，不過筆者聽後覺得改善效果不算明顯。</p><h2>降噪表現理想效果舒適</h2><p>至於降噪功能方面，cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 擁有 5000Hz 降噪頻率範圍，而且支援降低最多 45dB 噪音，同時在可以過濾噪音、風聲之餘，亦支援清晰話音技術。至於表現方面，筆者就試過佩戴著 Buds Pro 乘搭地鐵，並同時用它欣賞音樂，表現算是不錯，降噪效果不會太焗促，以免令用家感覺處身在密閉空間的同時，亦可以有效濾走外間噪音。另外，筆者用 Buds Pro 與朋友通話，效果亦十分不錯，即使在地鐵車箱內，對方仍可清晰聽到筆者話聲，效果令人滿意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-3.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Buds Pro 支援主動式降噪功能，在這價位的真無線耳機來説算是不太常見，而筆者試用過感覺不錯，有不俗的隔音效果，但同時又不會太焗促，以這價位的真無線耳機而言算是有驚喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234575" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00608-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00608-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00608.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，耳機上的收音咪亦支援清晰話音技術，筆者試過在地鐵車箱內與別人通話，對方也可清晰聽到筆者所説的內容。</p><h2>功能不多偏向基本</h2><p>最後功能方面，説是 Buds Pro，它基本上就真的只是一款真無線耳機，就是用來聽歌、睇戲時聽音效或者通話的耳機，其他功能不多。另外，操控方面，依然是採用在耳機機身透過觸控方法控制的方式，使用上亦十分方便，靈敏度亦高。此外，它亦支援 IP54（只限耳機）生活防水防塵功能，亦支援 Google 及 Microsoft 的快速配對模式，整體算是十分基本：未有驚喜但不算令人失望。至於使用時間方面，單是耳機最長可提供 11 小時音樂播放時間，而配合充電盒可提供最長 39 小時音樂播放，以入門級真無線耳機來説表現算是合格以上。即使沒電，使用充電盒為耳機充電 10 分鐘，已可為耳機帶來 5 小時音樂播放時間，算是不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164926-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164926-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164926.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲透過觸控模式就可以用手指在耳機耳柄位操控各功能，十分直覺化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234577" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-4.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果用家有安裝 Nothing X APP，亦可以在 APP 內調校耳機觸控不同次數對應操控哪種功能，可將操控個人化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-5.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，雖然 Buds Pro $400 有找，但它依然支援低延遲模式，同樣有驚喜。</p><h2>總結：定價抵玩表現符合預期</h2><p>總括來説，今次 cmf by Nothing 推出的 Buds Pro 真無線耳機，整體表現算是中規中矩：設計固然出色吸睛，降噪效果亦十分理想，但其他功能只屬基本，音質上雖然高音及人聲表現不俗，但官方標榜的低音表現卻是很一般，亦未支援任何無線音效標準。當然，作為一款 $400 有找，而且具有一定設計風格的真無線耳機，在如此抵玩的定價下，其實 Buds Pro 的表現也是符合預期，甚至已是比預期要理想，所以這些缺點，也不算是太大問題了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164802-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164802-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164802.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/cmf-by-nothing-watch-pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】cmf by Nothing Watch Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　屏幕　操控體驗　使用時間開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/cmf-neckband-pro-cmf-buds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 兩款無線耳機   CMF Neckband Pro、CMF Buds With ANC 發表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/23/cmf-by-nothing-neckband-pro/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 兩款無線耳機，確認 3 月 5 日與 Phone (2a) 一同發表</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/cmf-by-nothing-buds-pro-review/review-2/">【評測】cmf by Nothing Buds Pro　外形　佩戴感　音質　降噪　功能開箱評測</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
